room_title: Escape room "The Quest" by Escape The Room Oregon in Eugene
room_description: The Kingdom needs your help. Merlyn has been kidnapped by the evil sorceress, Morgana and King Arthur has been poisoned. You are the last hope to save the kingdom from certain doom. Merlyn has hidden away the holy grail- the only thing that can save Arthur in his time of need. Find the Grail, save the King who will save Merlyn, and in turn save the kingdom. Join us on this epic adventure... The Quest.
